<i>adverb</i>: 흥청망청 [흥청망청] <br>
<ul>
<li><i>adverb</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>흥청망청 [흥청망청]</dt><br>
<dd>1. carousingly; exultingly</dd><br>
<dd>매우 재미있거나 즐거워서 마음대로 즐기는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>A word describing the manner of enjoying oneself without inhibition, out of joy and excitement.</dd><br>
<dd>2. lavishly; extravagantly</dd><br>
<dd>돈이나 물건 등을 마구 쓰는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>A word describing the manner of spending money or things carelessly without saving.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>